<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka mawhna puokgik leh lei dahum hi,
 Thangvan ka et leh ziechun lut ka nuom;
 Van In nuom achun gitlohna umlo,
 Hungin ti a ei sapna Aw ka za'i.

[V2]
 2. Zie gam thiengtho leh lopi tak achun,
 Migilo ka hi ka ding ngam na dem;
 Zie Lalchutphah vam lopi ma achun,
 Mahleh va naih di'n khutin ei sam hi.

[V3]
 3. Nicheng in Van lampi chuh ka ngaihtuoh,
 Mahleh gitlohna'n nicheng in ei zui;
 Ka nakhang in thu kipahum ka za'i,
 &quot;Kisik in, haiin hing inla&quot; ei tii.

[V4]
 4. Ka zak hi Lalpa Isu Aw ahi,
 A khut in ei ban hi ei pui dingin;
 A thisan in, gitloh cheng a khuhmang,
 Lalchutphah maah dembei in ei kawih.

[V5]
 5. Kitupna Lalpa, kei di'n dawngin la,
 Na titna zalin kipahman keia;
 Linglukhuk Na khu'i keima'n Lallukhuk,
 Na thihna kei di'n hinna a hung hii.

[V6]
 6. Ka hun bat Lalpa hun din zo puo'ng ka,
 Mahleh lunggil in a theih chan pie hen;
 Ka pumin ka kipie'i ka lungthim tawh,
 Nei ngaihdamna chuh ka hengilh thei puoi.</lyrics>
<title>WEARY OF EARTH AND LADEN</title>
<hymn_number>270</hymn_number>
</song>